  "instructions": [
    "In a molcajete, toast the cumin, coriander, and paprika over medium heat for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the onion, ginger, and garlic to the molcajete and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the ground beef to the molcajete and cook, breaking it up with a spoon, until it is no longer pink.",
    "Stir in the fermented jang and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add the salt, black pepper, and dates to the molcajete and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving dish and top with toasted almonds.",
    "Serve warm, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
  ],
